duties_responsibilities.duty: Assemble materials for customer orders, receive new and returned products, and maintain safety and quality standards within the warehouse.
Operate forklifts, transfer materials, and handle outgoing and incoming product.
Document and record product movement, inventory, and customer returns in the warehouse management system.
Maintain warehouse cleanliness, safety, and organization, including routine maintenance tasks.
Adhere to safety guidelines, wearing protective equipment as required, and performing physical work activity duties.

education_certification.credential: High school diploma or equivalent. Forklift certification.
